data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home. With a 2-car garage and an expansive fenced yard, you'll have the space you need for both relaxation and entertainment. The thoughtfully designed layout offers a seamless flow, providing an inviting atmosphere for gatherings and everyday living. This home is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts, offering a generously sized yard for gardening, play, and relaxation. Located in a desirable neighborhood, convenience meets serenity in this remarkable property. Your new chapter begins here! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming residence your own!Schedule your tour today!
